Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.76,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a glittering shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:07.36,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts dried by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:10.87,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's stage is a giant mansion!\NMy rival Heiji also plays a big role!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.44,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
